    <h1>Gutter Cleaning in Richmond — Reliable Protection for Coastal Homes</h1>

    <p>Richmond’s flat terrain, coastal air, and frequent rainfall create constant pressure on residential drainage systems. When gutters fill with leaves, seeds, and wind-driven debris, water cannot move away from the roofline efficiently. In a city where many homes sit close to sea level, even minor drainage issues can lead to long-term moisture concerns.</p>

    <p>Clean Gutters Crew (CGC) provides professional gutter cleaning services across Richmond to help homeowners prevent water intrusion, protect exterior materials, and maintain structural integrity throughout the year. Our team understands how humidity, ocean exposure, and seasonal storms impact local properties.</p>

    <p>We serve Steveston, Broadmoor, Seafair, Terra Nova, Ironwood, Shellmont, Hamilton, and surrounding neighbourhoods. Whether your home is near the waterfront, exposed to coastal winds, or surrounded by mature landscaping, we adapt our cleaning approach to match the environment.</p>

    <h2>Why Gutter Maintenance Matters in Richmond</h2>

    <p>When drainage systems are blocked, rainwater can spill over the edges and collect around the foundation. In low-elevation areas, this increases the risk of soil saturation and interior dampness. Overflow can also affect siding, soffits, trim boards, and exterior finishes. Over time, untreated moisture contributes to material breakdown and expensive structural repairs.</p>

    <p>Consistent maintenance reduces these risks and keeps your property protected during heavy Pacific storms.</p>

    <h2>Our Cleaning Process</h2>

    <p>CGC performs a detailed service that includes complete debris removal, downspout clearing, water-flow testing, and a visual system inspection. We identify early signs of wear, loose sections, or drainage concerns before they become larger issues.</p>

    <p>Using professional-grade equipment, we work efficiently while protecting roofing materials, landscaping, and surrounding surfaces. The property is left clean and orderly once the service is complete.</p>

